1
00:00:10,220 --> 00:00:12,300
[SOUTH WIND KNOWS]

2
00:00:12,380 --> 00:00:18,540
♪My heart flipped when a dynamic
flashed between us someday♪

3
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:20,380
♪Guided by instinct♪

4
00:00:20,540 --> 00:00:24,660
♪We feel the same reason,
harboring a special feeling underneath♪

5
00:00:24,820 --> 00:00:27,780
♪Amidst the ecstatic shock♪

6
00:00:27,900 --> 00:00:30,900
♪I begin to doubt what I see♪

7
00:00:31,140 --> 00:00:36,380
♪I can't believe you made me compromise♪

8
00:00:37,060 --> 00:00:40,100
♪The world you're sick of♪

9
00:00:40,300 --> 00:00:43,060
♪I look into it thoroughly♪

10
00:00:43,260 --> 00:00:45,340
♪How lucky I am to console you♪

11
00:00:45,580 --> 00:00:48,940
♪When you suffer alone♪

12
00:00:49,140 --> 00:00:54,940
♪Yet I realize♪

13
00:00:55,140 --> 00:01:00,100
♪I cannot let go
of the love I hold onto tightly♪

14
00:01:00,300 --> 00:01:03,300
♪As I venture into the world
from a mundane life♪

15
00:01:03,580 --> 00:01:06,980
♪You show up at the exact moment♪

16
00:01:07,300 --> 00:01:09,740
♪My ambition♪

17
00:01:09,940 --> 00:01:12,420
♪Puts an end to this aimless journey♪

18
00:01:12,620 --> 00:01:15,580
♪The familiar light of pursuit
shines into my heart♪

19
00:01:15,860 --> 00:01:18,660
♪From the starting point♪

20
00:01:36,140 --> 00:01:41,380
[South Wind Knows]

21
00:01:41,500 --> 00:01:45,380
[Episode 31]

22
00:01:46,910 --> 00:01:47,510
Son,

23
00:01:48,710 --> 00:01:50,190
don't think too much.

24
00:01:50,750 --> 00:01:52,870
You'll recover for sure

25
00:01:52,910 --> 00:01:54,030
as long as you have enough rest.

26
00:01:54,790 --> 00:01:56,030
When you're discharged,

27
00:01:56,670 --> 00:01:58,630
I'm gonna take you somewhere warm

28
00:01:58,750 --> 00:01:59,790
to live for some days.

29
00:02:00,030 --> 00:02:01,350
You can recuperate properly.

30
00:02:02,590 --> 00:02:03,870
I know what I'm dealing with.

31
00:02:05,390 --> 00:02:06,030
Mom,

32
00:02:09,110 --> 00:02:10,270
you know it too.

33
00:02:11,950 --> 00:02:13,390
I know medicine.

34
00:02:15,670 --> 00:02:17,110
Medicine is broader than you think.

35
00:02:18,230 --> 00:02:20,030
There are so many possibilities.

36
00:02:22,270 --> 00:02:24,110
Just let the bodyguards at the door go.

37
00:02:25,670 --> 00:02:26,350
No.

38
00:02:27,510 --> 00:02:29,270
I won't let her keep badgering you.

39
00:02:38,230 --> 00:02:38,870
Fine.

40
00:02:41,030 --> 00:02:41,950
I'll make them leave.

41
00:02:43,830 --> 00:02:45,110
One more thing.

42
00:02:50,230 --> 00:02:50,910
I'm listening.

43
00:02:52,110 --> 00:02:54,270
Don't ever give Zhu Jiu a hard time again.

44
00:03:02,670 --> 00:03:03,470
Only if

45
00:03:07,270 --> 00:03:08,910
she won't hurt you...

46
00:03:12,870 --> 00:03:14,910
She never hurt me.

47
00:03:30,950 --> 00:03:32,670
I'll keep my word.

48
00:03:35,350 --> 00:03:38,430
I'll find a liver donor
for her grandmother.

49
00:03:40,910 --> 00:03:41,550
Okay.

50
00:03:46,110 --> 00:03:48,070
Be it Zhu Jiu or Zhizhi,

51
00:03:51,550 --> 00:03:53,590
just don't bother with them anymore.

52
00:04:09,230 --> 00:04:09,950
This time,

53
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:14,790
it's all my fault that you got injured.

54
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:22,190
Go home now.

55
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:25,550
I'm a little sleepy.

56
00:04:25,790 --> 00:04:27,110
I wanna sleep.

57
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:48,550
Okay.

58
00:04:54,550 --> 00:04:55,950
Have a good rest.

59
00:05:06,190 --> 00:05:07,150
You can go now.

60
00:05:07,550 --> 00:05:08,870
No need to come again.

61
00:05:26,420 --> 00:05:30,340
♪I'm wondering what I've lost♪

62
00:05:33,060 --> 00:05:37,700
♪Our love is still drifting♪

63
00:05:38,820 --> 00:05:41,500
♪It drifts past
the doorstep of happiness♪

64
00:05:42,180 --> 00:05:44,660
♪Into the depths of my heart♪

65
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:51,020
♪And brushes against your silhouette♪

66
00:05:51,860 --> 00:05:54,740
♪What makes you♪

67
00:05:54,860 --> 00:05:58,380
♪make up your mind♪

68
00:05:59,340 --> 00:06:05,340
♪To put on this show♪

69
00:06:05,700 --> 00:06:07,860
♪One more word♪

70
00:06:08,100 --> 00:06:12,100
♪Only makes it harder for me to believe♪

71
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:14,580
♪Carefully losing it♪

72
00:06:14,860 --> 00:06:17,940
♪Will look more sincere♪

73
00:06:18,180 --> 00:06:22,100
♪Than grasping it tight♪

74
00:06:23,220 --> 00:06:28,060
♪Only when loneliness congratulates me♪

75
00:06:29,780 --> 00:06:34,740
♪Do I realize time is unkillable♪

76
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:38,660
♪Are you waiting for me♪

77
00:06:38,980 --> 00:06:41,940
♪Are you not satisfied
to be a mere passer-by♪

78
00:06:42,340 --> 00:06:44,740
[Little Bunny]

79
00:06:44,740 --> 00:06:48,500
♪I'm gonna make it an epic story
with the rest of my life♪

80
00:06:48,660 --> 00:06:51,420
♪What makes you♪

81
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:55,380
♪make up your mind♪

82
00:06:55,980 --> 00:07:01,860
♪To put on this show♪

83
00:07:02,420 --> 00:07:04,540
♪Put in more effort♪

84
00:07:04,820 --> 00:07:08,580
♪And you'll suffer a little less♪

85
00:07:08,940 --> 00:07:11,140
♪My true heart♪

86
00:07:11,420 --> 00:07:14,740
♪Has never given up♪

87
00:07:14,860 --> 00:07:18,660
♪On loving you♪

88
00:07:39,190 --> 00:07:39,630
Mr. Fu,

89
00:07:40,110 --> 00:07:41,790
we've received the compensation
from the cold chain company.

90
00:07:43,470 --> 00:07:44,590
This is this month's transaction details

91
00:07:44,670 --> 00:07:45,870
provided by the Finance Department.

92
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:47,590
There's a transaction
to an overseas account,

93
00:07:48,150 --> 00:07:49,910
which is exactly half the compensation
from the cold chain company.

94
00:07:49,910 --> 00:07:53,660
[Gao Minna, Personal, 10,000,000]

95
00:07:54,710 --> 00:07:56,350
Was it wired to
one of his family's accounts?

96
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:57,070
Yes.

97
00:07:57,190 --> 00:07:57,990
His wife's.

98
00:08:00,870 --> 00:08:03,110
Make sure to collect
a solid chain of evidence.

99
00:08:03,470 --> 00:08:04,110
Yes.

100
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:05,870
Mr. Fu,

101
00:08:07,270 --> 00:08:10,270
why were you sure
that Jiang Jun would do this?

102
00:08:13,830 --> 00:08:14,950
Do you still remember

103
00:08:15,630 --> 00:08:17,070
for what reason

104
00:08:17,430 --> 00:08:18,910
he left the Marketing Department?

105
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:21,150
I do.

106
00:08:25,110 --> 00:08:25,790
Let go of me!

107
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:26,630
Let go!

108
00:08:27,470 --> 00:08:28,230
Fu Xizhou,

109
00:08:28,830 --> 00:08:29,990
you don't even dare to show up, huh?

110
00:08:30,430 --> 00:08:32,670
You let her subordinate take the blame
when you dared not mess with my aunt.

111
00:08:33,940 --> 00:08:34,700
Now tell me,

112
00:08:35,390 --> 00:08:37,180
who gives her the right to drive me away?

113
00:08:40,550 --> 00:08:42,390
You think this company is a bank?

114
00:08:43,060 --> 00:08:44,550
And everybody must play along with you?

115
00:08:44,910 --> 00:08:46,110
It's just a few dozen grand.

116
00:08:46,390 --> 00:08:47,630
I'll repay it in days.

117
00:08:48,110 --> 00:08:49,710
Are you desperately
trying to get rid of me?

118
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:01,830
Jiang Jun,

119
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:04,670
I'm trying to save you,

120
00:09:05,870 --> 00:09:07,750
in case you make bigger trouble

121
00:09:08,470 --> 00:09:09,630
that even your aunt
won't be able to save you.

122
00:09:09,790 --> 00:09:10,950
Give me a break.

123
00:09:11,110 --> 00:09:11,950
I'm telling you,

124
00:09:12,350 --> 00:09:14,110
if not for the sake of my cousin Yunshen,

125
00:09:14,510 --> 00:09:15,630
I would've slapped you.

126
00:09:19,390 --> 00:09:20,110
Me too.

127
00:09:21,470 --> 00:09:22,350
I would've done the same.

128
00:09:30,470 --> 00:09:32,310
He was so at ease with his mistakes.

129
00:09:32,910 --> 00:09:34,630
He never thought he was wrong.

130
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:36,190
Besides,

131
00:09:36,710 --> 00:09:38,390
he didn't get any severe punishment.

132
00:09:39,110 --> 00:09:40,670
So we don't need to get him cornered.

133
00:09:41,470 --> 00:09:42,550
He'll get himself into that naturally.

134
00:09:53,190 --> 00:09:55,830
Do you know
how much I've been missing you?

135
00:09:56,150 --> 00:09:57,190
You didn't answer the phone.

136
00:09:57,390 --> 00:09:58,820
And they wouldn't let me see you.

137
00:09:59,550 --> 00:10:00,270
But,

138
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:01,950
this is the first snow of this year.

139
00:10:02,270 --> 00:10:04,110
I'm so happy that

140
00:10:04,510 --> 00:10:05,830
we meet each other again on this day.

141
00:10:06,430 --> 00:10:07,830
Do you have anything to say to me?

142
00:10:10,110 --> 00:10:11,430
There's nothing to say.

143
00:10:13,310 --> 00:10:14,390
Are you cold?

144
00:10:15,510 --> 00:10:16,670
Bear with me a little.

145
00:10:17,110 --> 00:10:18,350
This is kinda my occupational habit.

146
00:10:18,630 --> 00:10:21,270
I'm always worrying
if my patients are cold.

147
00:10:22,710 --> 00:10:24,390
This is this year's first snow.

148
00:10:25,750 --> 00:10:27,150
It's nice to come out here to watch it.

149
00:10:30,830 --> 00:10:32,590
When I went to pick you up just now,

150
00:10:32,710 --> 00:10:34,310
I saw that the bodyguards were gone.

151
00:10:34,670 --> 00:10:35,990
You convinced your mom?

152
00:10:40,310 --> 00:10:41,070
Yunshen,

153
00:10:41,870 --> 00:10:43,590
are you not feeling well somewhere?

154
00:10:49,230 --> 00:10:50,390
What exactly is wrong with you?

155
00:10:54,190 --> 00:10:54,910
Zhu Jiu,

156
00:10:56,870 --> 00:10:58,030
we should break up.

157
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:07,750
Is this the side effect of the treatment?

158
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:08,910
I'm not joking.

159
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:13,870
A good relationship
makes people feel happy.

160
00:11:16,150 --> 00:11:17,350
But us being together

161
00:11:17,910 --> 00:11:18,790
brought each other

162
00:11:18,830 --> 00:11:20,470
more misfortune than happiness.

163
00:11:23,030 --> 00:11:24,550
Your mom just met me.

164
00:11:25,110 --> 00:11:26,710
Are you saying this to me now

165
00:11:26,990 --> 00:11:28,870
because of my grandmother's liver donor?

166
00:11:30,910 --> 00:11:31,990
You're overthinking.

167
00:11:33,430 --> 00:11:35,070
I simply want it to stop.

168
00:11:37,150 --> 00:11:39,150
You think I'll believe that?

169
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:46,430
I'm getting engaged with Zhizhi soon.

170
00:11:48,830 --> 00:11:50,470
I didn't want to tell you.

171
00:11:53,470 --> 00:11:55,830
You think I'll buy this one?

172
00:11:59,670 --> 00:12:01,070
My mom got suspended.

173
00:12:01,990 --> 00:12:03,830
My brother and her are fighting
to take control of the company.

174
00:12:04,110 --> 00:12:05,630
I need Zhou family's support.

175
00:12:06,510 --> 00:12:07,230
Yunshen,

176
00:12:09,710 --> 00:12:11,390
if today's the first day I know you,

177
00:12:12,110 --> 00:12:14,270
maybe I'll believe everything you said.

178
00:12:14,670 --> 00:12:16,510
But I've been through so much with you.

179
00:12:17,390 --> 00:12:19,190
I know perfectly well who you are.

180
00:12:20,030 --> 00:12:23,230
You would've joined the fight
if you wanted to.

181
00:12:23,470 --> 00:12:24,630
You won't wait until now.

182
00:12:24,950 --> 00:12:27,910
Not to mention
give up our relationship for it.

183
00:12:33,630 --> 00:12:35,470
If it's because of
my grandmother's liver donor,

184
00:12:36,190 --> 00:12:37,590
I can figure out some other way.

185
00:12:38,630 --> 00:12:40,990
I hope that you won't make
such decisions on your own again.

186
00:12:41,950 --> 00:12:43,470
This is our business.

187
00:12:47,310 --> 00:12:48,830
You know my health conditions.

188
00:12:50,870 --> 00:12:54,190
You mean the complications
after the surgery?

189
00:12:54,830 --> 00:12:55,790
You already knew?

190
00:12:58,550 --> 00:12:59,710
I was so worried about you.

191
00:13:00,150 --> 00:13:01,190
But I couldn't see you.

192
00:13:01,350 --> 00:13:03,350
So I went to ask your doctor-in-charge.

193
00:13:05,390 --> 00:13:06,470
You're a doctor.

194
00:13:09,550 --> 00:13:11,750
You should know quite well my conditions.

195
00:13:12,110 --> 00:13:13,870
I'm now someone

196
00:13:13,990 --> 00:13:15,430
who may die any minute.

197
00:13:15,870 --> 00:13:17,270
Being together with me

198
00:13:20,750 --> 00:13:22,430
will only waste your time.

199
00:13:35,430 --> 00:13:37,110
But nobody knows
what will happen in the future.

200
00:13:37,310 --> 00:13:38,990
Can you not be so sure of it?

201
00:13:41,110 --> 00:13:42,590
When I was in a coma,

202
00:13:45,470 --> 00:13:47,270
I had a long dream.

203
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,310
I dreamt that we were married.

204
00:13:53,390 --> 00:13:54,390
We had a baby.

205
00:13:55,070 --> 00:13:55,870
We quarreled.

206
00:13:57,190 --> 00:13:57,910
We fought.

207
00:14:05,430 --> 00:14:06,590
Our hair turned gray.

208
00:14:08,100 --> 00:14:09,470
Our teeth fell out.

209
00:14:14,430 --> 00:14:15,230
Perhaps

210
00:14:16,710 --> 00:14:18,630
I wanted such a life too much.

211
00:14:21,150 --> 00:14:21,910
That's why I felt extremely sad

212
00:14:23,750 --> 00:14:25,070
when I woke up

213
00:14:25,630 --> 00:14:27,190
and realized I'd be gone

214
00:14:30,310 --> 00:14:31,710
before you did,

215
00:14:34,590 --> 00:14:37,470
and you'd bear these pains

216
00:14:39,550 --> 00:14:41,830
all by yourself.

217
00:14:45,110 --> 00:14:46,150
I know that

218
00:14:47,150 --> 00:14:48,750
you may meet...

219
00:14:51,510 --> 00:14:52,830
someone else.

220
00:14:54,190 --> 00:14:54,910
This way,

221
00:14:55,950 --> 00:14:58,310
you'll have a peaceful life.

222
00:14:59,150 --> 00:14:59,990
In the future,

223
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:06,670
you'll have a proper family.

224
00:15:07,590 --> 00:15:09,550
Stable and happy.

225
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:14,750
But all this.

226
00:15:17,590 --> 00:15:19,710
I can't even promise you the least.

227
00:15:34,630 --> 00:15:35,430
Yunshen,

228
00:15:38,390 --> 00:15:39,430
you know what?

229
00:15:41,310 --> 00:15:43,270
I'm not afraid of any of what you said.

230
00:15:44,870 --> 00:15:46,950
What I'm afraid of is that
we're clearly in love,

231
00:15:48,310 --> 00:15:50,710
but we don't cherish our time together.

232
00:15:56,870 --> 00:15:58,270
This thing between us

233
00:16:00,310 --> 00:16:01,390
is precious.

234
00:16:02,390 --> 00:16:03,510
Can you not

235
00:16:05,870 --> 00:16:07,870
throw it away so quickly,

236
00:16:11,030 --> 00:16:11,790
alright?

237
00:16:13,740 --> 00:16:17,020
♪You know that I care for you♪

238
00:16:17,620 --> 00:16:20,820
♪There's one thing I can tell you♪

239
00:16:21,260 --> 00:16:28,580
♪I love you, I love you everyday♪

240
00:16:29,500 --> 00:16:36,940
♪All I wanna do is to love you to the world's end♪

241
00:16:36,990 --> 00:16:38,030
I'm sorry, Zhu Jiu.

242
00:16:43,980 --> 00:16:48,380
♪You know that I care for you♪

243
00:16:48,540 --> 00:16:52,020
♪There's one thing I can tell you♪

244
00:16:52,220 --> 00:17:00,260
♪I love you, I love you everyday♪

245
00:17:00,460 --> 00:17:07,100
♪All I wanna do is to love you my girl♪

246
00:17:07,580 --> 00:17:12,620
♪Never, ever gonna give you up my love♪

247
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:17,820
♪Forevermore♪

248
00:17:19,380 --> 00:17:26,700
♪Girl, I never ever gonna give you up my love♪

249
00:17:28,300 --> 00:17:31,700
♪Forevermore♪

250
00:18:03,990 --> 00:18:04,790
Miss Tao,

251
00:18:06,350 --> 00:18:08,110
please have the curtains

252
00:18:08,150 --> 00:18:09,230
and carpets laundered.

253
00:18:10,150 --> 00:18:11,110
-Okay.
-And the flowers.

254
00:18:11,670 --> 00:18:12,590
Replace them with fresh ones.

255
00:18:12,870 --> 00:18:13,790
You got it.

256
00:18:14,910 --> 00:18:15,630
Ms. Jiang,

257
00:18:15,790 --> 00:18:17,510
you're in a good mood today, huh?

258
00:18:19,350 --> 00:18:21,350
Some problems are solved.

259
00:18:21,830 --> 00:18:22,790
I'll get busy now.

260
00:18:34,270 --> 00:18:35,230
Hi, Meiyun.

261
00:18:35,670 --> 00:18:36,430
(Shuning,)

262
00:18:36,910 --> 00:18:38,710
(I asked Mrs. Wang for afternoon tea.)

263
00:18:39,070 --> 00:18:40,470
(She said
she hadn't seen you for so long.)

264
00:18:40,710 --> 00:18:41,630
(Are you free)

265
00:18:41,630 --> 00:18:42,230
(to join us?)

266
00:18:42,390 --> 00:18:42,950
Sure.

267
00:18:43,270 --> 00:18:44,230
Wait for me.

268
00:18:44,350 --> 00:18:45,670
I'll be on my way after I get ready.

269
00:18:45,830 --> 00:18:46,350
Okay.

270
00:19:01,310 --> 00:19:01,750
Head nurse.

271
00:19:02,030 --> 00:19:02,510
Jin.

272
00:19:02,790 --> 00:19:04,150
Is Mr. Fu's IV drip done?

273
00:19:04,270 --> 00:19:04,790
Yes.

274
00:19:04,830 --> 00:19:05,430
He's sleeping now.

275
00:19:05,550 --> 00:19:07,030
Good. Go back to the Nurse Station now.

276
00:19:07,110 --> 00:19:07,670
Okay.

277
00:19:55,710 --> 00:19:57,150
Hey Siri, come out.

278
00:19:57,430 --> 00:19:59,750
Hi, how may I help you?

279
00:20:00,070 --> 00:20:01,110
You came out when I asked you to.

280
00:20:01,230 --> 00:20:02,190
Where's your pride?

281
00:20:02,190 --> 00:20:04,100
♪A single clue♪

