292
00:20:28,470 --> 00:20:29,870
The road to true love is never easy...

293
00:20:30,110 --> 00:20:31,030
Do you know that

294
00:20:31,150 --> 00:20:32,510
love is the business of two people?

295
00:20:32,590 --> 00:20:34,430
