304
00:21:12,620 --> 00:21:19,060
♪You feel my pain♪

305
00:21:19,860 --> 00:21:20,940
♪No reason♪

306
00:21:21,100 --> 00:21:26,620
♪For those meaningless winds
to pass by me♪

307
00:21:26,780 --> 00:21:29,060
♪It hurts secretly♪

308
00:21:29,620 --> 00:21:33,340
♪When you don't love me♪

309
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:36,260
♪No matter where you are♪

310
00:21:36,380 --> 00:21:40,460
♪I'll always be with you♪

311
00:21:41,220 --> 00:21:47,660
♪Why must we miss out on each other
when our hearts are broken?♪

312
00:21:48,460 --> 00:21:52,180
♪Imitating others who flinch and escape♪

313
00:21:52,340 --> 00:21:54,900
♪After love sparks fade away♪

314
00:21:55,140 --> 00:22:00,980
