366
00:24:54,190 --> 00:24:55,270
It's fine.

367
00:24:55,990 --> 00:24:57,350
I won't blame him.

368
00:24:58,230 --> 00:24:59,630
I just feel sorry for him.

369
00:24:59,950 --> 00:25:03,750
He can't go home
even for the Spring Festival.

370
00:25:48,830 --> 00:25:50,750
I'm a bit tired now, honestly.

371
00:25:54,830 --> 00:25:56,950
Try not to fall ill.

372
00:25:57,750 --> 00:26:00,230
Once you are ill, you become weak.

373
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:02,990
Let me support you to your room.

374
00:26:03,310 --> 00:26:04,430
No need.

375
00:26:04,990 --> 00:26:07,430
Put the finished ones into the fridge.

376
00:26:08,270 --> 00:26:09,870
I'll have a little rest.

377
00:26:10,070 --> 00:26:11,430
When I get down here later,

378
00:26:12,070 --> 00:26:15,190
