387
00:27:12,870 --> 00:27:14,150
And your appetite is good too.

388
00:27:14,750 --> 00:27:16,110
I suppose you'll be discharged soon?

389
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:18,550
Still need some days.

390
00:27:24,590 --> 00:27:25,310
Grandpa,

391
00:27:26,710 --> 00:27:27,790
I'm so sorry

392
00:27:28,230 --> 00:27:31,070
