in the hospital.

393
00:27:33,030 --> 00:27:34,630
As long as we're together,

394
00:27:35,030 --> 00:27:36,550
I'm fine with having it anywhere.

395
00:27:37,790 --> 00:27:38,470
Yeah.

396
00:27:39,150 --> 00:27:40,270
The family being together

397
00:27:40,390 --> 00:27:41,590
