398
00:27:44,510 --> 00:27:45,110
Oh.

399
00:27:48,990 --> 00:27:50,270
The lucky money.

400
00:27:54,710 --> 00:27:55,270
Grandpa,

401
00:27:55,870 --> 00:27:58,110
