when I'm already at this age?

402
00:27:59,870 --> 00:28:01,150
As long as you're not married,

403
00:28:01,350 --> 00:28:03,670
I'll give you this every year.

404
00:28:04,790 --> 00:28:05,390
Take it.

405
00:28:12,070 --> 00:28:12,990
Thanks, Grandpa.

406
00:28:14,430 --> 00:28:15,670
Speaking of getting married...

407
00:28:15,830 --> 00:28:16,350
Dad,

408
00:28:16,950 --> 00:28:19,230
how about we ask
the Zhou family for dinner

409
00:28:19,470 --> 00:28:20,910
after Yunshen is discharged

410
00:28:21,070 --> 00:28:22,430
