411
00:28:24,110 --> 00:28:25,510
What's most urgent now

412
00:28:25,910 --> 00:28:27,470
is to let Yunshen recover.

413
00:28:27,830 --> 00:28:29,590
We'll talk about other things later.

414
00:28:30,510 --> 00:28:32,430
Yunshen and Zhizhi are both old enough.

415
00:28:32,630 --> 00:28:33,950
I think the two of them can perfectly...

416
00:28:34,030 --> 00:28:34,830
You know what?

417
00:28:36,230 --> 00:28:37,390
I'm having a food coma.

418
00:28:38,470 --> 00:28:39,390
Let's go home.

419
00:28:40,470 --> 00:28:41,110
Come on.

420
00:28:41,710 --> 00:28:42,510
Then Yunshen...

421
00:28:42,790 --> 00:28:44,310
I'll send grandpa back first.

422
00:28:45,190 --> 00:28:46,030
You eat more, okay?

423
00:28:46,510 --> 00:28:47,990
