You light up one as well.

427
00:29:20,910 --> 00:29:22,110
Okay.

428
00:29:25,590 --> 00:29:28,070
I didn't know you were so romantic!

429
00:29:32,150 --> 00:29:32,750
Yunshen,

430
00:29:33,510 --> 00:29:34,670
