437
00:29:49,870 --> 00:29:52,590
I hope that Yunshen
will be safe and healthy

438
00:29:52,670 --> 00:29:54,070
year after year.

439
00:29:57,150 --> 00:29:57,750
I get it.

440
00:29:58,670 --> 00:29:59,830
Every year afterward,

441
00:30:00,710 --> 00:30:01,870
I'll stay up with you

442
00:30:02,670 --> 00:30:03,670
to see in the New Year.

443
00:30:05,230 --> 00:30:09,110
Then let's do this
in our twenties, thirties,

444
00:30:09,230 --> 00:30:10,510
forties, fifties, sixties, seventies,

445
00:30:10,590 --> 00:30:12,510
eighties, and nineties.

446
00:30:14,830 --> 00:30:15,350
Okay.

447
00:30:21,350 --> 00:30:21,870
Pinky promise.

448
00:30:21,990 --> 00:30:24,230
Whoever lies is dung.

449
00:30:24,270 --> 00:30:24,950
Dung beetle.

450
00:30:26,470 --> 00:30:27,590
That's a deal.

451
00:30:28,110 --> 00:30:29,510
I won't go back on it.

