457
00:32:57,310 --> 00:32:57,910
No.

458
00:32:59,710 --> 00:33:01,390
I'm here to sit out
New Year's Eve with you.

459
00:33:03,670 --> 00:33:05,990
Remember what we promised each other?

460
00:33:07,950 --> 00:33:09,990
We'll celebrate

461
00:33:13,390 --> 00:33:14,430
