00:35:33,630 --> 00:35:34,310
Two.

492
00:35:36,430 --> 00:35:37,030
One.

493
00:35:45,580 --> 00:35:49,100
♪How long is it until the future?♪

494
00:35:49,700 --> 00:35:53,060
♪How worn out must this longing be?♪

495
00:35:53,340 --> 00:35:56,500
♪I love you, I love you♪

496
00:35:56,740 --> 00:36:00,700
♪Hiding from freedom♪

497
00:36:01,420 --> 00:36:04,460
♪Every time we get in touch♪

498
00:36:04,900 --> 00:36:08,900
♪So many ifs waiting for me♪

499
00:36:09,230 --> 00:36:10,070
Yunshen,

500
00:36:14,030 --> 00:36:15,270
happy New Year.

501
00:36:15,980 --> 00:36:20,460
♪You've been possessed
by optimism relentlessly♪

502
00:36:20,630 --> 00:36:21,630
Happy New Year.

503
00:36:22,070 --> 00:36:22,830
Zhu Jiu.

504
00:36:24,150 --> 00:36:25,230
Happy New Year.

505
00:36:25,670 --> 00:36:26,510
Yunshen.

506
00:36:27,940 --> 00:36:32,140
♪This pattern♪

507
00:36:32,500 --> 00:36:38,980
