524
00:38:54,550 --> 00:38:55,670
You finish them as soon as possible.

525
00:38:56,470 --> 00:38:58,150
They won't last very long.

526
00:38:59,190 --> 00:39:00,710
As for these wontons,

527
00:39:00,790 --> 00:39:03,790
