560
00:41:00,070 --> 00:41:01,230
Put them away.

561
00:41:03,510 --> 00:41:05,710
I'll keep them for you then.

562
00:41:15,870 --> 00:41:16,590
Look.

563
00:41:19,950 --> 00:41:21,670
This snow is so heavy.

564
00:41:24,110 --> 00:41:25,230
This is so nice.

565
00:41:29,830 --> 00:41:32,470
The next year
will definitely be a bumper one.

566
00:42:07,460 --> 00:42:11,020
♪I see you in a dark corner♪

567
00:42:11,340 --> 00:42:14,660
♪With vulnerability overwhelming you♪

568
00:42:14,900 --> 00:42:16,980
♪Biting your lips
and facing away from me♪

569
00:42:17,260 --> 00:42:21,220
♪You break the walls of stubbornness♪

570
00:42:21,940 --> 00:42:25,020
♪Once more, another sundown
swiftly passes by♪

571
00:42:25,220 --> 00:42:30,460
♪Love is like a lie at the end
of the century♪

572
00:42:30,700 --> 00:42:36,380
♪That almost fools me♪

573
00:42:38,420 --> 00:42:40,860
♪No matter where you are♪

574
00:42:41,020 --> 00:42:45,940
♪I'll always be with you♪

575
00:42:46,140 --> 00:42:52,860
♪A kiss can heal this wrecked world♪

576
00:42:53,060 --> 00:42:59,820
♪If there is a slight possibility
of avoiding loneliness♪

577
00:43:00,140 --> 00:43:06,500
♪Let me endure the heavy rainfall
with you♪

578
00:43:06,700 --> 00:43:10,820
♪If there is a slight possibility♪

579
00:43:10,980 --> 00:43:16,940
♪The moon that once shone for me
should stay radiate♪

580
00:43:17,180 --> 00:43:23,060
♪You'll regain happiness
when you are true to yourself♪

581
00:43:25,100 --> 00:43:27,700
♪I never thought you♪

582
00:43:27,900 --> 00:43:32,540
♪Would feel the way I do♪

583
00:43:32,740 --> 00:43:39,500
♪You feel my pain♪

584
00:43:39,660 --> 00:43:46,580
♪No reason for those meaningless winds
to pass by me♪

585
00:43:46,780 --> 00:43:53,500
♪When the meaningless things hit me♪

586
00:43:53,620 --> 00:43:56,060
♪No matter where you are♪

587
00:43:56,220 --> 00:44:01,140
♪I'll always be with you♪

588
00:44:01,340 --> 00:44:07,860
♪Why must we miss out on each other
when our hearts are broken?♪

589
00:44:08,580 --> 00:44:15,140
♪Imitating others who flinch and escape
after love sparks fade away♪

590
00:44:15,300 --> 00:44:24,140
♪All I yearn for
is the warmth deep within you♪
